title: My Boss Bajrangbali
subTitle: A corrupt politician kills Anji's parents and plans to demolish a temple. Later, Lord Hanuman takes human form to help Anji fight the politician.

title: Nene Raju Nene Mantri
subTitle: Driven by his wife's wishes, Jogendra ventures into politics. However, as he climbs the ladder of influence, he risks becoming a heartless power-monger.

title: Bicchugatthi
subTitle: In the 16th-century Chitradurga, Baramanna Nayaka rises against the tyrant Dalavayi Muddanna, determined to restore peace and protect his land from exploitation.

title: Krishna Ka Badla
subTitle: A disillusioned actor, Babu, reluctantly joins a drama troupe for one last play. He teams up with journalist Meera and together they uncover a dangerous conspiracy that treatens them both.

title: Ruslaan
subTitle: Ruslaan, a terrorist's son, undergoes a major life change when an anti-terrorism officer adopts him. Determined to fix his bad reputation, Ruslaan becomes an intelligence agent.

title: 777 Charlie
subTitle: Dharma, a broken man drowning in despair, finds his world transformed when he rescues Charlie, an abused pup. Later, they embark on a journey of hope and redemption.

title: Seetharama Kalyana
subTitle: Arya, a righteous man, falls in love with a small-town woman named Geetha, unaware of the obstacles that lie ahead for both of them.

title: Vishal In Laatti Charge
subTitle: A police constable lands in grave danger when he gets trapped by a dangerous gang in a building with his sick son. He must strive to defeat the villains and escape to safety.

title: Shershaah
subTitle: Vikram Batra, a young man, dreams of becoming a soldier and falls in love with Dimple. Soon after his training, he climbs the military ranks and contributes to India's victory in the Kargil war.

title: Power Unlimited 2
subTitle: Karthikeya, a man who is devoted to his family, faces a huge challenge as his violent and turbulent past begins to resurface.

title: Custody
subTitle: A police constable's life takes a drastic turn when he is entrusted with producing a criminal in court. While the mobster remains under his custody, Shiva must dodge every threat to keep him alive.

title: Custody
subTitle: A police constable's life takes a drastic turn when he is entrusted with producing a criminal in court. While the mobster remains under his custody, Shiva must dodge every threat to keep him alive.

title: Romeo
subTitle: Arivu desires a real love connection but ends up with Leela, who marries him out of family obligation. However, despite their differences, he tries his best to win her over.

title: Baaz: A Bird in Danger
subTitle: The police are out on the hunt for a serial killer who targets beautiful women. Their luck changes when a woman who is in love with one of the suspects joins the search.

title: Ek Zakhmi Romeo
subTitle: Ananya loves her best friend, Surya, while he falls for another woman, Pooja. However, after his heartbreak, Surya is too late to realise who truly loved him as Ananya rejects him.

title: Satya Gang
subTitle: Satya and Raj, who are orphans, own a garage and make a living out of it. However, their lives turn tragic when a notorious gang commit numerous murders and make them the culprits.

title: Saptagiri Express
subTitle: A happy-go-lucky actor is forced to do his father's job after his unexpected demise. However, when he realises his father was murdered, he sets out to exact vengeance.

title: Agent Chanakya
subTitle: Arjun, a highly sought-after RAW agent, is known for his skills at catching some of the most hardened criminals. However, he falls in danger when he goes after Ibrahim Qureshi, a terrorist.

title: Mawali Raaj
subTitle: In order to obtain a family of their own, two young children of two single parents devise a plan to bring them together.

title: Raja Hindustani
subTitle: Raja, a taxi driver, falls in love with Aarti, a rich girl and marries her against her parents' wishes. Later, her stepmother tries to create differences between the couple.

title: Yudh Ek Jung
subTitle: Chandu, a supermarket employee, encounters trouble when he decides to help Indu, an aspiring actress, and gets embroiled in a murder case.

title: Kuberaa
subTitle: Following a tycoon's discovery of a rare oil reserve, a compassionate beggar gets trapped in the dangerous mechanisms of his rapacious scheme.

title: Jawaan
subTitle: Yellapragada Jai, an honest man, faces challenges when his childhood friend, Keshava, becomes a criminal. To protect his country, Jai puts everything on the line to thwart Keshava's perilous plans.

title: Jawaan
subTitle: Yellapragada Jai, an honest man, faces challenges when his childhood friend, Keshava, becomes a criminal. To protect his country, Jai puts everything on the line to thwart Keshava's perilous plans.

title: Main Hoon Dandadhikari
subTitle: Following his father's death, a man gives up on his dream to become a film-maker and joins the police force. He then attempts to track down a psychopathic killer who targets schoolgirls.

title: Zed Plus
subTitle: Aslam, a villager who runs a small business, accidentally meets the prime minister of India, who grants him special security on his request. Soon, he starts chasing political ambitions.

title: Crazy Singh
subTitle: Bittu, a village simpleton, falls in love with a modern Saumya. Chaos ensues when their contrasting families meet to fix their marriage.

title: Darling 2
subTitle: Five friends on a holiday in Valparai find their getaway turning eerie when they sense the haunting presence of a friend who recently died by suicide.

title: Main Hi Raja Main Hi Mantri
subTitle: A moneylender is living a happily married life. However, when his wife is insulted by the village sarpanch's wife, he focuses all of his energy on becoming a powerful politician.

title: Raththam
subTitle: While investigating his friend's murder, Ranjith, a journalist, unearths the sinister network responsible for a series of crimes.

title: Meri Taqat Mera Faisla
subTitle: A young man follows in his father's footsteps by working for the welfare of the people living in his district. However, a corrupt politician threatens to thwart his plans.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi
subTitle: A man and a woman develop a great bond after the latter arrives in Hyderabad. However, they realise their love for each other when the woman's marriage is arranged to a person of her parent's choice.

title: Secret Agent
subTitle: Forced to live a detached life in the Andaman Islands, a secret agent comes across a woman pursued by debtors and tries to protect her.

title: Sita Ram
subTitle: Ram, a young boy, lives in a monastery waiting for Sita to return and take care of him. However, Sita returns, years later, but with an ulterior motive.

title: Naa Saami Ranga
subTitle: A man gains great notoriety in his village for his unmatched strength and brutal nature, which makes him a target of antisocial elements with a ruthless agenda.

title: Cadaver
subTitle: When two surgeons mysteriously get murdered by Vetri, a prisoner, the responsibility of locating his accomplice falls on the shoulders of a pathologist.
